    • Method Detail

      • enhanceRemoteProcessing

        void enhanceRemoteProcessing(SimpleJavaParameters parameters)
                      throws ExecutionException
        Our recommended practice is to work with third-party api from external process in order to avoid potential problems with the whole ide process. For example, the api might contain a memory leak which crashed the whole process etc.

        This method is a callback which allows particular external system integration to adjust that external process settings. Most of the time that means classpath adjusting.

        Parameters:
        parameters - parameters to be applied to the slave process which will be used for external system communication
        Throws:
        ExecutionException
